middle.section:
&kw-2119;

The terminology for describing YANG data models is found in
.

section.sourcecode:
typedef dns-class-name {
  type enumeration {
    enum IN {
      value 1;
      description
        "Internet (IN)";
      reference
        "RFC 1035";
    }
    ...
  }
  ...
}

typedef rr-type {
  type union {
    type uint16;
    type rr-type-name;
  }
  description
    "This type allows for referring to a DNS resource record type
     using either the assigned mnemonic name or numeric value.";
}

