back.section:
&ed-hint-rfcno;
This appendix contains an XSLT 1.0 stylesheet that is intended to be used for generating the initial revision of the "iana-dns-class-rr-type" YANG module. This is achieved by applying the stylesheet to the XML version of the IANA registry "Domain Name System (DNS) Parameters" that was current at the time when this document was published.
Using the ubiquitous xsltproc tool, the YANG module text can be generated with this command:
$ xsltproc iana-dns-class-rr-type.xsl dns-parameters.xml
&xslt;
